Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. We have this training \Nso early in the morning because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I am doing it for my own sake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, \NI'll have to earn my own Knight promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After getting me a knight promotion,\Nyou claim to actually be training for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said. \NBesides, this is a pleasant walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you like it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm training even harder than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it even at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The next game is just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All I do is training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you are only satisfied with perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.62,Song,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy your stay with a fresh coffee \N Coffee - 400 \NOmelet rice - 680 \NToast (with salad) - 500 \N Neapolitan (with salad) - 680 \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when you two are concerned about being fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We exercise a lot these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Writing is a tiresome manual labor. \NIt requires a lot of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! We'll have two "Mornings." With milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With milk? Don't you know my coffee \Nis supposed to help you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed it myself already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, with milk it seems more nutritious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Milk is required to build a strong body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to care about you body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it’s the brain where the fat tends to accumulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, relax. Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you two are somehow weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, you are always weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding, just kidding. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Photos and materials \Nrelated to pachislot development history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything from generation zero \Nto the latest models is covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the ones that never made it to the production line are featured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we making a new series?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, just start working \Non whatever you come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This time we have a lot to sort out, \Nso you can look at the materials yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Bonus" is active.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you a favor, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please check the reader's enquêtes for today, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How many thousands are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 2600 sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer those number in coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:57.63,Song,,0,0,0,,Come \NSee \NConquer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This place does not go easy on visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the point. \NIt's perfect for our training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.14,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\b0\pos(401.256,46)\an4\fscy85}number of Bigs {\c&H46DD68&}000\N {\c&HFFFFFF&}number of games {\c&H46DD68&}000\N\N\N\N\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}number of Bigs {\c&H3F35B8&}000\N {\c&HFFFFFF&}number of games {\c&H3F35B8&}000
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.14,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\b1\pos(390.11,46)\an6}Today's \N\NYesterday's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You kiddin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:07.64,Song,,0,0,0,,{\b1}{\fs36\pos(390.11,46)\an6}Today's\N\NYesterday's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:07.64,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\b0\pos(401.256,46)\an4\fscy85}number of Bigs {\c&H46DD68&}000\N {\c&HFFFFFF&}number of games {\c&H46DD68&}000\N\N\N\N\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}number of Bigs {\c&H3F35B8&}000\N {\c&HFFFFFF&}number of games {\c&H3F35B8&}000
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All the machines here have a factory data reset!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way to pick from this variety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we talking about?\NAren't we the proud slotters of Slothium?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Congratulations!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, even a grandma is able to hit Big here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you turn down a place like this, \Nhow can you expect to defeat a Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Touché.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To give this place a chance, \NI'll start with 5 test games.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on it again? \NStart with speaking to a machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, cause pachislot is a living being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear it clearly. \NYour heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What, a Bar scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes won't fail me! \NAiming for a Bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a secured Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it another try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Secured!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your neighbor's delight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's your turn to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the case. \NYou are desperate for a good slotter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I will give you the help you desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to have any diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, spread your hands wide \Nand jump straight into my warmest cuddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. You are maturing. \NYour body is thriving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the prize balls won today, \Nthose guys took 83 in just 8 games!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy settings are only for getting used to the machine. \NHard settings are for seasoned players.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. By the time you get accustomed, \Nthe match is already lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Umei, memo, memo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure was a fine game you showed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,True, so true! Especially with our hands \Nfull of those bonus souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can already see my grandson's happy face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to bother thanking. \NIt was a training after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That is indeed so. \NThen, Ginya, I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will see those young men tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally. \NIt's a training after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we look forward \Nto seeing you tomorrow as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally. \NIt's a training after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, did you hear what this guy just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The customer is king, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Any progress yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all just a bit messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The editor-in-chief has been collecting those \Nin utter chaos it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, amazing! Take a look at this, Ishibashi! \NWhat a peculiar one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It has 5 reels! But why would they need so much reels?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you need anything, ask me. \NThere's another box in the storage room. Good luck!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood! So this one is related to the \Ngeneration zero stuff. But what about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fushina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you eventually manage to acknowledge \Nyour hatred's true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to follow my footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and climb up to me your own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you take this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- No... But what does it have to do with development...  \N- Emy! Can you make me a coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and master?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He certainly looks similar to the Drum Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A famous machine developer quits his job \Nto {\i1}travallier{\i0} as a coffee shop master you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out for a quick interview, \Nif you excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this smells like an interesting article.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, forgot something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Better yet! \NYuri, you should see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a scoop, a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I be interested? \NIt's a pachislot scoop after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, fine! Just take a look at this photo. \NAin't that spicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And this - it's a pachislot machine, isn't it?\NYou don't see photos like this very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's gonna be \Nthe next Spinning Gears' exclusive pachislot front-pager.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I found this among the raw materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're busy as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Keeping myself busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, I was just planning to ask you \Nto enlighten me on that matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shibaura Futoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, it's almost gym time. \NYou're free to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Ginya, good luck with the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We may still have customers. \NCome after the closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. \NIn that case, see you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, Mr. Shibaura. \NReady to tell me the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, let me see it once again \Nso I can recall properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So many memories. \NIt was 17 years ago I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. It was Master after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow I knew it the moment I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That accounts for your familiarity with the Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On this photo, we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,still in the age when you can live \Nfueled by nothing but dreams and passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We attempted on creating a machine \Nof a brand new kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A new kind of machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The ideal machine, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the one on this photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still remember it clearly even to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one truly happy period.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm driving a bike you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, you've become quite good at those gimmicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimmicks... What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was willing to tell you whatever I know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I was also hoping \Nyou'd help me by complementing the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Complementing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,With that paper plane at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I took those at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This one doesn't have Master in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is... Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... This one... is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the man next to you \Nis my associate Shinbashi Kojiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A co-developer of that machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbashi Kojiro... Shinbashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. That is your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Father? Then, Master and my father \Nhave been developing a pachislot machine together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So Master have been working on it \Nfrom the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I helped building it \Nbut only in the final stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you see it. But from my perspective, \Nit's not a good occasion for chit-chatting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy anyway since you agreed to talk about it.\NBesides, no one told me anything about this guy before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That paper plane...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kojiro used to make those for you \Nevery now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember. \NI do remember how to fold it myself though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We had my sister's photos in plenty \Never since she was a toddler.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But not a single one of me \Nbefore I'm 3 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So among those, \Nthere's gotta be a lot of pictures of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a vile guy, I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is, our piblings despised him so much, \Nthey didn't even want to keep his photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the mom's photos were not spared. \NWe only had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And a Buddhist temple photo at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this man, our mom is now \None sheet away from living in our memory only.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems pretty vile a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It is indeed so that Kojiro didn't make it in time \Nneither for Sakura's childbirth nor for her deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you just said \Nhe didn't make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, dad was trying to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He never showed up — neither when Mai was born \Nnor when sister Sakura was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a vile man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But have no worries — \Nhe was duly punished for abandoning you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He died as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just three months after my sister's demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kojiro can by no means \Nbe considered a vile man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it yourself on the photo, \Nwhere Sakura has your little sister inside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Sakura and Kojiro \Nare smiling sincerely and happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the dead, say nothing but good, \Nisn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the dead? \NKojiro you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Immediately after the mother's demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,After Sakura's death, we've been developing \Nthe machine together for at least a year more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,my father can still be alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,15 years ago we finished developing the machine \Nand I could finally retire from pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I decided to visit him again some time later, \Nthe place was already abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,From then on, \Nwe both had our own careers to pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I've never heard a word of him being dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain, out there somewhere, \Nhe is still kicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My real father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out you didn't die after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even to this day, \Nyou never tried to tell us you're still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You never even tried to come and see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! \NToday seems to be a very nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what we have \Nin coming broadcasting schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning! I'll have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi, are you alone today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My counterpart deserted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a one-day break?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably playing pachislot somewhere again, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At this hour, nothing is open yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Master, have you seen Ginya since... \N- Oumi, are you good with milk again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't make it too light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Father was developing \Npachislot machines for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The very things \NI became so keen about in Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No use. It's turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's peculiar, \Nseeing Ginya go AWOL like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's home, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya? Ginya! You there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last one... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I won yesterday, \Ndoesn't mean I'll prevail today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wise words one can use to redeem his defeat.\NUmei, memo, memo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What of it is true? \NAnd what is not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the day of the game. \NWasting another one worrying will get me nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Any minute now, the most prominent members \Nwill compete for a Knight title in a promotion game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally happening. Our most recent members \Nare about to enter the life-changing fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you expect to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi has been riding the waves \Nquite well lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Game starts in 5 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,4...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi. Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Otonashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing, goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Is this Otonashi guy okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he lost his nerve \Nbecause this game is different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is alive, can my dad still \Nbe working with pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it to me, even if dad is still alive? \NWhy do I keep getting that feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I not got over it a long time ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really that vulnerable a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he become too agitated?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, if you were alive... Dad... Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom was laughing... Dad too... And me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were everyone laughing \Nwith such happy faces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a vile man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... I don't get it. \NWhere is the truth here? Where is the lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred is overflowing your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over for you.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.69,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.71,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.69,0:21:34.27,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:34.29,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.27,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,5,,Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.22,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.21,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,800)}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,800)}Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflection.
